text: Kuzminovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Kadyrgulovsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 41 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 38 km from Davlekanovo, 5 km from Kadyrgulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Kuzminovka, Davlekanovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
